summary: I got tired of drawing mermaids. I was going to try to keep going, but I’m really just not that into mermaids, sorry guys. 😛 But...
caption: I got tired of drawing mermaids. I was going to try to keep going, but I’m really just not that into mermaids, sorry guys. 😛 But I’m pretty happy with how this turned out, even though her eyes turned out way bigger than intended. I used @jadakoi as a reference! 😉 Done with a mix of Copic markers, Staedtler Triplus Pens, Faber Castell Polychromos color pencils, Stabilo pastel pencils, and Copic opaque white ink on Muji mini sketchbook!
